1 nh ngha

Market Basket Analysis l 1 phng php phn tch vi mc ch l tm ra cc t hp sn phm hay c khch hng mua cng nhau

V d: khch hng mua m tm th thng cng mua c tht b kh v trng

2 Cc khi nim c bn

  • Rule: Nu A, th B \[{i_{1},i_{2},...} => {i_{k}}\]
  • SupportGi tr Support ca 1 sn phm hoc 1 t hp sn phm l t l gia s giao dch cha sn phm hoc t hp sn phm vi tng s giao dch
    • V d: Mt ca hng trong thng 1 c 100 khch mua hng. Trong 50 khch hng mua sn phm A, 75 khch hng mua sn phm B, v 25 khch hng mua c sn phm A v B
      • Support(sn phm A) = 50%
      • Support(Sn phm A, sn phm B) = 25%
  • Confidence: Xc sut c iu kin th hin kh nng khch hng mua sn phm A cng s mua sn phm B. Gi tr confidence ca 1 rule l kh nng rule s xy ra 1 giao dch mi trong c cha cc sn phm v bn tri ca rule \[Confidence (i_{m} => i_{n}) = \frac{support(i_{m}\frown i_{n})}{support (i_{m})}\]
    • V d: Confidence (sn phm A , sn phm B) = 25/50 = 50%
      • Tc l nu 1 ngi mua sn phm A, th xc sut h cng mua sn phm B l 50%
  • Lift: Nu khch hng mua sn phm A th kh nng h mua sn phm B s tng ln bao nhiu % \[Lift(i_{m} => i_{n}) = \frac{support(i_{m}\frown i_{n})}{support(i_{m}) * support (i_{n})} = \frac{Confidence (i_{m} => i_{n})}{support (i_{n})}\]
    • Lift c th cho 3 loi gi tr
      • Lift > 1: tc l nhng sn phm v tri ca rule s lm tng kh nng xy ra ca nhng sn phm v phi ca rule (2 sn phm b tr)
      • Lift < 1: tc l nhng sn phm v tri ca rule s lm gim kh nng xy ra ca nhng sn phm v phi ca rule ( 2 sn phm thay th c cho nhau)
      • Lift = 1: Cc sn phm v tri v v phi xut hin c lp vi nhau, khng rt ra c kt lun v rule
    • V d: Lift (sn phm A , sn phm B) = 50/75 = 0.67
      • Tc l nu 1 ngi mua sn phm A, th kh nng h mua B gim 33%

3 Cch lm Market Basket Analysis

  • S dng 2 gi package R: library (arules), library (arulesViz)
  • Cc bc thc hin
    • B1: i d liu dataframe sang dng transaction
      • S dng hm as() v split()
    • B2: V itemFrequencyPlot xem nhng sn phm no c mua nhiu nht, chim bao nhiu % ca c tp d liu
    • B3: Dng hm apriori() tm ra cc rules
    • B4: Trc quan ha d liu
library(arulesViz)
plot(rules, method = "graph", interactive = TRUE, shading = NA)

5 Mt vi lu

  • Cn loi b cc rule tha (redundant)
    • Rule A c gi 1 rule tha, khi rule A l tp m ca 1 rule khc, v rule A c lift bng hoc thp hn so vi rule .
    • Tc l: Vi 2 rule {A,B,C} {D} v {A,B} {D}, th {A,B,C} {D} l rule tha nu c lift thp hn so vi rule cn li
      • V d:
        • milk => bread (12% support , 85% confidence, 1.2 lift)
        • milk, flavor = Chocolate => bread (1% support, 84% confidence, 1.15 lift)
    • Cch b cc rule tha
subset.matrix <- is.subset(rules, rules)
subset.matrix[lower.tri(subset.matrix, diag = T)] <- NA
redundant <- colSums(subset.matrix, na.rm = T) >= 1
which(redundant)
rules.pruned <- rules[!redundant]
rules <- rules.pruned
rules %>% sort(by = "lift") %>% head %>% inspect
